c3\\u00afc Bad\\u00c3\\u00a9 and Lucas Beltr\\u00c3\\u00a1n.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's Lo\\u00c3\\u00afc Bad\\u00c3\\u00a9 was HYPED after muscling Argentina's Lucas Beltr\\u00c3\\u00a1n off the ball \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00a4pic.twitter.com/pZezn4EP7T  The animosity between thetwo national teamshas been boiling for a long time.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999924812564821, \"rank\": 7.517709939242656e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994528460343285, \"rank\": 0.000530484263603441, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They faced off in an absolute classic during the 2022 World Cup final, but things got much more contentious last month.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Argentina won Copa Am\\u00c3\\u00a9rica, avideo of its players singing an offensive songabout French players of African heritage surfaced.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994528460343285, \"rank\": 0.000530484263603441, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argen